    "title": {
      "en": "Report of the Comptroller and Auditor General of India on Welfare of Building and Other Construction Workers for the year ended 31 March 2023"
    },
    "summary": {
      "en": "This Report contains the results of the Performance Audit of ‘Welfare of Building and Other Construction Workers’ in Delhi covering the period 2019-20 to 2022-23.  Major audit findings include shortcomings in identification and registration of establishments engaged in construction activities and registration and renewal of construction workers; deficiencies in database of registered construction workers; inadequacies in providing welfare measures to construction workers etc."
